data.description: Previous buyer back out of the deal based upon agreement of sale contingency.  Are you ready to fire your landlord?  Is it time to leave the safety of the nest of your parent's pad? Or maybe it is time for an upgrade or downsizing. Whatever your current situation. Welcome to what could very well be your NEW HOME!  This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom rowhouse in the desirable Mt. Airy neighborhood of Philadelphia. This lovely home boasts a large, well manicured front lawn and patio, perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. As you step inside, you'll notice the new laminate flooring on the first floor, which adds a modern touch to the space. The second floor features new carpets, providing a cozy and comfortable feel. The updated kitchen with granite countertops, decorative backsplash, and new flooring means you can move right in and started preparing delicious meals. The central air system ensures that you'll be comfortable year-round. The garage has been converted into a half bathroom and additional storage space, providing even more room for you and your family to spread out. This home is conveniently located near shopping, dining, and public transportation, and other neighborhood amenities. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own!
